<|startoftext|>I came for lunch and ordered a veggie dish to share with my wife. This was great. I had never had a veggie dish at a Japanese restaurant, but I'm so glad I found one here. I loved the flavors and texture they put out. Definitely a great option when you want to try something different and not share with all of your Japanese friends (I lived for the old times). If you're planning to eat here, check out their specials and come prepared.<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>Food is great. Super fast! The staff is very nice!!! The manager is so nice!! Definitely a place that deserves 5-star service!! Thank you so so much for making our day!<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>I've been here twice now. I ordered the breakfast burritos and they were both very good - I would definitely order the veggie burrito again. I also got the frito, which was delicious, and the avocado toast was fantastic. I can't wait to go back and try the rest of the burritos!<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>I would not recommend this company to anybody!   The manager was unprofessional!!  I had been there twice after asking for a new carpet.  The man who took my report was a nag to customer service and just made it worse!.  He said that it's a two-year lease - two consecutive leases.  He said that was what he had been in to do in the first place!  I understand the place needs work but the management can do better!<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>The service here is very good and the place is very clean. So, my review is probably biased on that score.\nI had the turkey wrap and the chicken sandwich. I went with the mild version and it was still pretty great. I also liked the garlic knots that I got. I will say however, that when I get there and I sit down to eat my sandwich it sometimes gets a little too warm. It really starts to get soggy quite a bit when I put it on a warm plate. So that's probably what I love about the sandwiches...<|endoftext|>
<|startoftext|>As a woman with small to normal arms I know how to appreciate all the time spent at the gym doing cool stuff. But that's about it.  I never spent more than an hour in the door before it got too cold to go back. I really hate going back with my wife but this is the only thing I will do.<|endoftext|>
